title: Witzel first to receive UND Nurse Practitioner award (ND Center for Nursing)
text: ( Source : ND Center for Nursing ) For local Nurse Practitioner Gwen Witzel, her years of hard work have been noticed and recognized by her peers when she was awarded the University of North Dakota ( UND ) Nurse Practitioner Outstanding Alumni
